        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-100">
          This page covers the modded version of Super Bear Adventure. For the official game maintained by Earthkwak Games, see the <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Earthkwak.Platformer&hl=en" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Google Play release</a>.
        </p>

        <!-- Definition Card -->
        <div class="bg-game-green-50 border-l-4 border-game-green rounded-r-xl p-5 my-8">
          <strong class="text-gray-900">Definition — Super Bear Adventure Mod APK</strong>
          <p class="mt-2 mb-0">The Super Bear Adventure Mod APK is a modified Android version of the game. You get unlimited coins, all skins, and no ads from the start. The 3D platforming and exploration stay the same as the official v{SITE.download.version} game on Google Play.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entity Strip -->
      <EntityStrip />

      <!-- Key Takeaways -->
      <div class="my-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-game-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
          </svg>
          Key Takeaways
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-game-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Latest official patches</strong>: v12.1.5 fixes multiplayer invite codes; v12.1.4 fixed save corruption (see <a href="/blog/version-changelogs/" class="text-game-green hover:underline">changelog</a>).</span>
