          Understanding the difference helps you choose the right version. The official game on Google Play has over 100M+ downloads and a 4.4-star rating with 883K+ reviews. It's free but includes ads and requires grinding for coins to unlock cosmetics.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          <strong>Official app on Play Store:</strong> 100M+ downloads, 4.4★ (883K+ reviews), PEGI 3. Store listing updated {SITE.download.updated}. Developer: <a href="https://earthkwak.games/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Earthkwak Games</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Comparison Table -->
      <ComparisonTable />

