          <img src="/images/blog/changelogs.svg" alt="Super Bear Adventure v12.1.5 update — latest 2026 patches and improvements" width="800" height="450" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="rounded-2xl shadow-md w-full h-auto border border-gray-200" />
