        <ul>
          <li><strong>v12.1.5</strong>: Fixed multiplayer <strong>invite codes</strong> (current Play Store version)</li>
          <li><strong>v12.1.4</strong>: New invite format, copy/paste invites, and fixes for <strong>save file corruption</strong> that could wipe progress</li>
          <li><strong>v12.1.3</strong>: Lobby <strong>version number</strong> display, timer fixes, and cosmetic fixes</li>
          <li>Already in the game: <a href="/blog/the-hive-walkthrough/">The Hive</a> (since 2022), <a href="/blog/multiplayer-guide/">multiplayer</a> (since 12.0), and <a href="/blog/arcade-world-mini-games/">Super Bear Fighters</a> (since 12.1.0)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For the complete history, see our <a href="/blog/version-changelogs/">version changelog archive</a>.</p>

        <h2 id="exclusive-features">Exclusive Features of the Modded Version</h2>

