              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">You get unlimited coins and gems. Buy every hat, skin, and accessory whenever you want. Great if you want to enjoy the story without the coin grind.</p>
              <a href="/blog/super-bear-adventure-unlimited-money/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-game-green mt-3 hover:underline">Learn more <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" /></svg></a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-md overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all">
            <div class="relative w-full h-44 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-indigo-50">
