            </div>
            <div class="p-5">
              <h3 class="font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-2 text-lg">All Skins & Hats Unlocked</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Access every cosmetic item from day one. Skeleton Bear, Royal Cape, and all rare skins included. No need to grind or pay.</p>
              <a href="/blog/unlock-all-skins-hats/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-game-green mt-3 hover:underline">See all skins <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" /></svg></a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-md overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all">
            <div class="relative w-full h-44 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50">
              <img src="/images/features/no-ads.svg" alt="No advertisements — completely ad-free gameplay" width="800" height="600" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-5">
              <h3 class="font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-2 text-lg">No Advertisements</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Play without interruptions. Zero pop-ups, zero video ads, zero banner ads. Pure gameplay experience from start to finish.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-md overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all">
            <div class="relative w-full h-44 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50">
              <img src="/images/features/anti-ban.svg" alt="Anti-ban protection and security scanning" width="800" height="600" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-5">
              <h3 class="font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-2 text-lg">Anti-Ban Protection</h3>
