          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.875rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Ready to Download?</h3>
        <p style="color: #d1d5db; font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Super Bear Adventure Mod APK v{SITE.download.version}</p>
